year. Chris Klein made it 2-0 in the 32nd minute, also scoring on 
an assist from Radosavljevic. 
</P>
<P>
	Los Angeles (4-4) scored its only goal in the 37th minute, when  
Danny Pena took a cross from Cobi Jones and fired a left-footed 
shot off the underside of the crossbar and into the goal. 
</P>
<P>
	Chris Snitko made two saves in the last 10 minutes to preserve  
the win for Kansas City. 
