<HEADLINE>  Pope Makes Historic Romania Visit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BUCHAREST, Romania (AP) -- Pope John Paul II, saying the ``spring  
of hope has begun,'' joined the leader of Romania's Orthodox Church 
in calling for the healing of divisions within Christianity. 
</P>
