<CATEGORY> washington </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Mother's Day Anti-Gun Pledge </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	Text of the Mother's Day anti-gun pledge distributed Saturday at  
the White House: 
</P>
<P>
	--I will not give my child unsupervised access to a firearm.  
</P>
<P>
	--I will not allow my child to play in a home where guns are  
improperly stored. 
</P>
<P>
	--If I own a gun, I will unload it and lock it up and store the  
ammunition separately and securely. 
</P>
<P>
	--I will urge others, including my community leaders and  
political leaders, to do everything in their power to protect our 
children. 
</P>
