and a diplomatic solution to Kosovo. Guests: Li Zhaoxing, Chinese 
ambassador to the United States; Undersecretary of State Thomas 
Pickering and Gen. Wesley Clark, NATO supreme allied commander, 
Europe. 

</P>
<P>
                              *------	 

</P>
<P>
	CBS' ``Face the Nation'' -- Topics: Media violence and Kosovo.  
Guests: Sens. Joseph Lieberman, D-Conn., Sam Brownback, R-Kan., 
Hollywood producer Dick Wolf and Bruce Reed, White House domestic 
policy adviser. 

</P>
<P>
                              *------	 

</P>
<P>
	NBC's ``Meet the Press'' -- Topics: War in Kosovo, Chinese  
espionage and youth violence. Guests: Sens. John McCain, R-Ariz., 
Joseph Biden, D-Del., Richard Shelby, R-Ala., and Bob Kerrey, 
D-Neb.; Energy Secretary Bill Richardson; conservative activist 
Gary Bauer; National Rifle Association Executive Vice President 
Wayne LaPierre; Motion Picture Association of America President 
Jack Valenti; former Sen. Bob Dole and Vladislav Jovanovic, 
Yugoslav ambassador to the United Nations. 

</P>
