peace overture. Guests: House Minority Leader Dick Gephardt, D-Mo.; 
Vladimir Rachmanin, Russian Foreign Ministry spokesman; Vladislav 
Jovanovic, Yugoslav charge d'affaires; Undersecretary of State 
Thomas Pickering; Rep. John Kasich, R-Ohio, and NATO Secretary 
GeneralJavier Solana. 

</P>
