prospects and teen violence. Guests: Sens. Richard Shelby, R-Ala., 
John Kerry, D-Mass., and Kay Bailey Hutchison, R-Texas; Rep. Porter 
Goss, R-Fla.; James Brown of Fox Sports, and Reggie White, former 
NFL player and author. 
</P>
